comment: Smart Data models EDI Codeco schema adapted to DTDL from smartdatamodels.org. Source: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/smart-data-models/dataModel.MarineTransport/master/EdiCodeco/schema.json
description: A message by which a terminal, depot, etc. confirms that the containers specified have been delivered or picked up by the inland carrier (road, rail or barge). This message can also be used to report internal terminal container movements (excluding loading and discharging the vessel) and to report the change in status of container(s) without those containers having physically been moved. See [UN/EDIFACT - CODECO](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d19a/trmd/codeco_c.htm)

contents.name: alternateName
contents.comment: An alternative name for this item

contents.name: areaServed
contents.comment: The geographic area where a service or offered item is provided

contents.name: ata
contents.comment: Actual time of arrival or departure to/from Terminal. (ISO 8601 UTC format). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment DTM - C507 (2380)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl2380.htm)

contents.name: bookingCode
contents.comment: Booking Reference. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment RFF - C506 (1154)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl1154.htm)

contents.name: containerCarrierIdentification
contents.comment: Code identifying a party involved in a transaction. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment NAD - C082 (3039)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl3039.htm)

contents.name: containerIdentification
contents.comment: Containter identification. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment EQD - C237 (8260)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8260.htm)

contents.name: containerSeal
contents.comment: The number of a custom seal or another seal affixed to the containers. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment SEL - 9308](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl9308.htm)

contents.name: containerWeight
contents.comment: Weight of the container. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment MEA - C174 (6314)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl6314.htm)

contents.name: dataProvider
contents.comment: A sequence of characters identifying the provider of the harmonised data entity

contents.name: dateCreated
contents.comment: Entity creation timestamp. This will usually be allocated by the storage platform

contents.name: dateModified
contents.comment: Timestamp of the last modification of the entity. This will usually be allocated by the storage platform

contents.name: description
contents.comment: A description of this item

contents.name: destination
contents.comment: Final destination of the container (UN/LOCODE: United Nations Code for Trade and Transport Locations). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment LOC - C517 (3225)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl3225.htm) and [UN/LOCODE](https://unece.org/trade/cefact/unlocode-code-list-country-and-territory)

contents.name: destinationTransportType
contents.comment: Method of transport code (UN/ECE). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - C220 (8067)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8067.htm) and [UN/ECE - Rec 19](https://unece.org/trade/uncefact/cl-recommendations)

contents.name: dischargingPort
contents.comment: Port where the container is discharged (UN/LOCODE: United Nations Code for Trade and Transport Locations). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment LOC - C517 (3225)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl3225.htm) and [UN/LOCODE](https://unece.org/trade/cefact/unlocode-code-list-country-and-territory)

contents.name: fileName
contents.comment: File name of EDI Codeco message

contents.name: isContainerEmpty
contents.comment: Information about if the container is full or empty. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment EQD - 8169](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8169.htm)

contents.name: loadingPort
contents.comment: Port where the container is loaded (UN/LOCODE: United Nations Code for Trade and Transport Locations). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment LOC - C517 (3225)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl3225.htm) and [UN/LOCODE](https://unece.org/trade/cefact/unlocode-code-list-country-and-territory)

contents.name: messageRaw
contents.comment: Raw message of the EDI Codeco

contents.name: messageVersion
contents.comment: Version of the message type. See [UNTDID - D.95B - UNH - S009 (0052)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/trmd/codeco_d.htm#DSGI)

contents.name: name
contents.comment: The name of this item

contents.name: originTransportType
contents.comment: Method of transport code (UN/ECE). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - C220 (8067)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8067.htm) and [UN/ECE - Rec 19](https://unece.org/trade/uncefact/cl-recommendations)

contents.name: receiverIdentification
contents.comment: Interchange Recipient Identification. See [UN/EDIFACT - S003](https://unece.org/trade/uncefact/unedifact/part-4-Annex-B)

contents.name: release
contents.comment: Release number within current version number. See [UNTDID - D.95B - UNH - S009 (0054)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/trmd/codeco_d.htm#DSGI)

contents.name: senderIdentification
contents.comment: Interchange Sender Identification. See [UN/EDIFACT - S002](https://unece.org/trade/uncefact/unedifact/part-4-Annex-B)

contents.name: sentAt
contents.comment: Date and time of message has been sent represented by an ISO 8601 UTC format. See [UN/EDIFACT - S004](https://unece.org/trade/uncefact/unedifact/part-4-Annex-B)

contents.name: source
contents.comment: A sequence of characters giving the original source of the entity data as a URL. Recommended to be the fully qualified domain name of the source provider, or the URL to the source object

contents.name: travelReference
contents.comment: Conveyance reference number. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - 8028](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8028.htm)

contents.name: truckLicenseCode
contents.comment: License Plate of the Truck. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - C222 (8213)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8213.htm)

contents.name: vesselCallSign
contents.comment: Maritime call signs are call signs assigned as unique identifiers to vessels. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - C222 (8213)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8213.htm)

contents.name: vesselCarrier
contents.comment: Vessel carrier Identification (identification of party undertaking or arranging transport of goods between named points). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - C040 (3127)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl3127.htm)

contents.name: vesselImo
contents.comment: International Maritime Organization Number (a global forever UID). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - C222 (8213)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8213.htm)

contents.name: vesselMmsi
contents.comment: Marine Mobile Service Identity Number (a temporarily assigned UID, issued by that object's current flag state). See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - C222 (8213)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8213.htm)

contents.name: vesselName
contents.comment: Vessel Name. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment TDT - C222 (8212)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl8212.htm)

contents.name: vesselVoyage
contents.comment: Reference number of vessel voyage. See [UNTDID - D.95B - Segment RFF - C506 (1154)](https://service.unece.org/trade/untdid/d95b/uncl/uncl1154.htm)

contents.name: owner
contents.comment: A List containing a JSON encoded sequence of characters referencing the unique Ids of the owner(s)

contents.name: address
contents.comment: The mailing address
